 Victoria Kimani and Sarkodie in the studio Former Chocolate City signee, Victoria Kimani has teamed up with Ghanaian rapper, Sarkodie for a new song. The Kenya rapper teased her fans with an Instagram post of herself and Sarkodie in the studio. She wrote, “When we dropping this new chune @sarkodie ? ??” View this post on Instagram A post shared by KIMANI (@victoriakimani) It looks like whatever is brewing between this duo is going to be a banger! We can’t wait and we hope it drops soon! Don’t take your time guys!